keywords:
  - large language models
  - economic elasticities
  - belief elicitation
  - taxable income elasticity
  - optimal taxation
abstract: >-
  Elicitation harness, 6,630-run dataset, and paper studying the
  prompt-conditioned response distributions that 17 frontier large
  language models produce when asked about 26 economic elasticities
  under a fixed structured-output protocol with 15 repeated runs per
  model-quantity cell.
